===[[Pokémon Masters EX]]===
{{main|Barry (Masters)}}
Barry, in his {{game|Diamond and Pearl|s}} design, forms a [[sync pair]] with {{p|Piplup}} and its evolved forms {{p|Prinplup}} and {{p|Empoleon}}, along with {{p|Roserade}}, {{p|Heracross}}, {{p|Floatzel}}, and {{p|Infernape}} in [[Pokémon Masters EX]]. His Heracross is capable of [[Mega Evolution|Mega Evolving]]. Barry became a playable sync pair since the game's release, with him joining the {{player}} after completing the second chapter of the [[PML arc]]. 

Barry has also made notable appearances in the game's main stories, the PML arc, and the [[villain arc]].

